high_descs: Move to the shelves on the left across the room.
Pick up the remote control on top of the shelf.
Head to the lamp on the right.
Turn on the lamp with the remote.
anns.task_desc: Use the remote on the white shelf to turn on the lamp to the left of the couch.

high_descs: Walk towards the couch, turn left before reaching the couch, walk towards the right side of the shelves.
Take the remote control to the right of the box on the top of the shelves.
Turn right and go to the lamp next to the couch, put the remote control under the lamp shade.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp while holding a remote control.

high_descs: Walk forward and left around the coffee table to the shelf against the wall
Pick up the remote near the box from the shelf
Turn right and approach the floor lamp in the corner
anns.task_desc: Examine the remote under the light of the floor lamp
